hadiths[10]{hadithnumber,text}:
4217,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey aqeeqe key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala uqooq ko napasand farmata hai. (maloom hota hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney lafz aqeeqa ko achcha nahin samjha) us saail ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : jab hum mein sey kisi key yahan bacha paida ho to wo janwer zibeh karta hai. (hum to uskey mutalliq poochh rahey hain) aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney bachey ki taraf sey janwer zibeh karna chahey to wo ladkey ki taraf sey do puri bakriyan zibeh karey aur ladki ki taraf sey eik bakri. (Hadees key raawi) Dawud ney kaha ke mainey Zaid bin Aslam sey « اَلْمُکَافَأَتَانِ » ki baabat puchha to unhoney kaha : is sey murad do eik jaisi bakriyan hain jo b-yak waqt zibeh ki jaeyn.
4218,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sayedna Hasan aur Husen Raziallahu anhuma ki taraf sey Aqeeqa kya.
4219,"Hazrat Salman bin Aamir Zabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bachey ki taraf sey aqeeqa hona chahiye, lihaza janwer zibeh karo aur bachey sey mail kuchail door karo."
4220,Hazrat Umme-Kurz (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ladkey ki taraf sey do kamil bakrey zibeh kiye jaeyn aur ladki ki taraf sey eik.
4221,Hazrat Umme-Kurz (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ladkey ki taraf sey do kamil bakrey zibeh kiye jaeyn aur ladki ki taraf sey eik.
4222,"Hazrat Umme-Kurz (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas (Hudebiya mein) hazir hui taake aap sey qurbani key gosht key barey mein poochhun. mainey aap ko farmatey suna : ladkey ki taraf sey do bakriyan aur ladki ki taraf sey eik bakri zibeh karna lazim hai. koi harj nahin, muzakkar hon ya muannas."
4223,Hazrat Umme-Kurz (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ladkey ki taraf sey do bakriyan aur ladki ki taraf sey eik bakri (aqeeqa mein) zibeh ki jaey. wo (aqeeqe key janwer) nar hon ya mada (bakrey hon ya bakriyan) koi harj nahin.
4224,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Hasan aur Hazrat haseen Raziallahu anhuma ki taraf sey do do mendhey aqeeqe mein zibeh farmaey.
4225,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har bacha apney aqeeqe key iwaz girwi hota hai. saatwen din uski taraf sey janwer zibeh kya jaey, sar mundwaya jaey aur us ka naam rakha jaey."
4226,"Hazrat Habib bin Shaheed bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Muhammad bin Sirin ney kaha ke Hazrat Hasan Basri sey poochho , unhon sey aqeeqe key barey mein ye hadees kis sey suni hai? mein un sey puchha to unhoney farmaya : mainey ye riwayat Hazrat Samra (bin Jundub) (Raziallahu anhu) sey suni hai."
